# 🤖 Basic Chatbot

A simple rule-based chatbot built using Python that responds to predefined user messages.

## 📌 Features

- Interactive conversation
- Greeting responses
- Basic question answering
- Exit command support
- Easy to customize

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- Python 3

💬 Supported Commands
User Input	           Bot Response
hello / hi	           Hello!!
how are you	           I am fine. Thanks!!
what is your name	     My name is chatbot.
bye	                   Goodbye!

📚 Learning Outcomes
Functions in Python
String manipulation
Conditional statements
User interaction
Basic NLP concepts

